      <p><strong>Layer 2 — Klaviyo data depth.</strong> Predictive segments for replenishment readiness, subscription risk, bundle affinity. Pairs with Sequenzy when catalog and variant complexity justify profile pricing.</p>
      <p><strong>Layer 3 — Yotpo proof and loyalty.</strong> Reviews after education completes; loyalty tiers gated from stranger discount flows. Coordinates with replenishment — not same morning.</p>
