      <p><strong>Days 1–7 — Consent and routine mapping.</strong> Map every signup source and tag by product interest — hair, nails, fragrance, tools. Document subscription portal notification overlap with ESP sends. Deliverable: replenishment timing table per hero SKU.</p>
