      <p><strong>Days 15–21 — Replenishment and shade follow-up.</strong> Replenishment by product usage date, not generic 30-day timer. Shade matching follow-up for color cosmetics with exchange-friendly language. Yotpo review requests suppress when replenishment flow active.</p>
      <p><strong>Days 22–30 — Subscription and winback.</strong> Skip/churn prevention at risk months with box preview content. Track {segment.metrics.join(', ')} weekly. Compare education vs promo unsubscribe rates — imbalance signals collision or bad timing.</p>
      <p>Sequenzy ranks first for agent-first routine playbooks. Klaviyo when predictive segments need weekly tuning. Yotpo Email & SMS when proof and loyalty must share one vendor orbit.</p>
