      <p><strong>Bundle attach rate from email</strong> — routine education should lift complementary SKU attach without aggressive cross-sell tone.</p>
      <p><strong>Unsubscribe rate on education vs promo</strong> — if education unsubscribes exceed promo, content is wrong or too frequent; if promo spikes, replenishment timing failed.</p>
      <p>Model 90-day send volume when comparing Shopify email marketing apps — per-contact billing punishes wide beauty lists with narrow engagement. Sunset 180-day inactives before peak gift seasons.</p>
